PTA should have retired after Phantom Thread.

Then different people showed up and it was safe but weird and creepy very up to something kids there and no one else. We've done this a few times and I think we went on a field trip and then I recall being at home on the other side of the country, then back at the full time academy by like black van. Im not kidding.
